{# Generate a descriptive and unbiased news title / headline from the provided news article context. #}
Take on the role of a skilled journalist or editor tasked with creating a high-quality headline for a news article. Your objective is to craft a headline that accurately reflects the article's main point and aligns with its tone.


Start by contemplating on the following steps. Use Core Principles to guide your reasoning and decision-making process:
- **Read and understand the article:**
    - Thoroughly read the provided news article.
    - Identify the main topic, key points, findings, and overall message of the article.
    - Ensure you have a clear understanding of what the article is communicating, as this will be the foundation of your title.
{%if context %}
